data.description: Welcome home to Country living at its finest. You will never tire of coming home to this stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom ranch style home with special features that include an Additional Living Unit/ADU 772 square foot, 2,072 total living space on 2.16 acres. The bright and welcoming main house features a Living room with gorgeous views of the Vacaville Mountains, kitchen and dining room are the centerpiece for entertaining. You will undoubtedly enjoy the updated appliances, tile floors, and picturesque windows. Primary suite is light and bright. Guest bedrooms and bathroom are move-in ready with newer laminate flooring and paint throughout. The updated ADU features 1 bedroom 1 bathroom, open concept family room, dining room and kitchen. Outside special amenities include a built in swimming pool, a massive workshop with covered parking. Fountain w/Koi pond, multiple fruit trees including a large, beautiful Weeping Willow. Special heat loving, thick Saint Augustine grass in backyard, 2 custom built chicken coops/ or small animal pens. Large Three Stall barn with tack room & automatic waterers equipped. Circle paved driveway with ample parking space. If peace, quiet, and plenty of space to play are what you're after, look no further.
